high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go to the fridge
Slice the potato in the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge
Pick up a slice of potato from the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the microwave
Put the potato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the potato slice
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cook a slice, put it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room to the table, hang a right and go to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around, go to the wall, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, cut the rightmost potato that is in the fridge into slices.
Turn to the left, go to the sink that is on the right.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn to the right, go to the fridge that is on the left.
Remove a slice of potato from the fridge.
Turn around, go forward, hang a right, go to the microwave that is above the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave, turn it on to cook, remove the potato once it is done cooking.
Turn around and go to the wall, hang a left, go to the fridge.
Put the potato slice in the fridge in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked slice of potato in the fridge.
